Megumi Code — vendored fork of Charm Crush
===========================================

This directory contains a vendored and modified copy ("fork") of Charm Crush,
embedded into the mgm CLI so that `mgm megumi` runs as part of the single mgm
binary. It is internal MGM Laboratory tooling.

