Modifications made by MGM Laboratory
------------------------------------
The original source layout was preserved except that the upstream `internal/`
path segment was flattened into this package
(`github.com/MGM-Laboratory/mgm-cli/internal/megumi/crush/...`) and import paths
were rewritten accordingly. Upstream tests, testdata, and the standalone
`main.go` were omitted. Behavioural changes:

  * Memory/context-file convention rebranded to MEGUMI.md (config defaults).
  * Added cmd.Run(ctx, args) as an in-process launcher (no os.Exit).
  * Added an optional in-process credential hook (agent.CredentialProvider) that
    injects the live Megumi broker credential as the x-api-key header per
    request; nil by default (upstream behaviour).
  * Added a MEGUMI_LOCK provider lockdown that restricts the agent to the single
    Megumi broker provider.

Telemetry (PostHog) and provider auto-update are disabled at runtime by the
embedding CLI via configuration/environment; no upstream endpoints are contacted.
